answer: The Council Decision (98/135/EC) was made on 18 December 1997. It concerns the provisional application of a Memorandum of Understanding on trade in textile products between the European Community and the Arab Republic of Egypt. The decision allows for the provisional application of the Memorandum from 1 January 1998, pending formal conclusion and reciprocal provisional application by Egypt. The decision was published in the Official Journal of the European Communities and was signed by F. Boden, President of the Council.
